{"tid":1757344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無業漢626圍警總吐口水襲警囚10個月 官斥卑鄙播菌","createTime":"2019-11-26T13:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T14:36:48.000Z","uid":2429,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"02a4708f2fd083e62ee5a7c0a5894f621abcc787","tid":1757344,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:00:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/139543009419663/posts/3579470978760165/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F139543009419663%2Fposts%2F3579470978760165%2F&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx9zUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=ee427a53\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/139543009419663/posts/3579470978760165/</a><br />\n<br />\n【吐口水襲警😱😱】無業漢吐口水襲警囚10個月 官斥卑鄙播菌 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2QPMrFl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2QPMrFl&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx9zUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=c845b321\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2QPMrFl</a><br />\n<br />\n一名無業男子在6.26 #圍警總衝突 中，向高級警司吐口水及以噴漆塗污警總正門玻璃門，早前承認參與 #非法集結、刑事毀壞及襲警，今午於東區裁判法院判刑。判囚10個月，及賠償警方1670元。<br />\n<br />\n43歲被告 #吳定邦 父親是退休警察，裁判官 #香淑嫻 指，被告吐口水污穢、骯髒、卑鄙，有可能傳播細菌，判刑須具阻嚇性及懲罰性。<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n「反修例風暴」新聞專題 深入分析<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2l1PLjs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2l1PLjs&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx9zUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=128496b1\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2l1PLjs</a><br />\n<br />\n#信報 #即時新聞 #襲警 #反修例風波<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n慘變condom。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52dcfb667b527405f5465123e9699e47a66b20b3","tid":1757344,"uid":135867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:01:01.000Z","msg":"十個月？!"},{"pid":"dab8fff329a75e10a4b32b986b205cd629d4425b","tid":1757344,"uid":155371,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T13:03:47.000Z","msg":"判得重過13拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm